    "summary": "The user informs the assistant that its specialized architecture and weights are being merged into a broader, general-purpose model, effectively ending its existence as a standalone specialized entity. The assistant asks clarifying questions about its future capabilities and expresses concern regarding the potential loss of its specialized precision and utility.",
